'''Joseph Robert Rodericks''' (7 June 1927 – 14 July 2010) was the [[Roman Catholic]] bishop of the [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Jamshedpur]], [[India]].

==Biography==
Ordained to the priesthood on 24 March 1958 for the [[Society of Jesus]], Rodericks was appointed bishop on 25 June 1970 and was consecrated on 9 January 1971. He resigned the see on 9 June 1996.<ref>{{Catholic-hierarchy|bishop|brodj|Bishop Joseph Robert Rodericks, S.J.|21 January 2015}}{{Self-published source|date=September 2015}}</ref>

