'''''Sikh Phulwari''''' is a monthly [[Punjabi language|Punjabi]] and [[Hindi]] magazine of the [[Sikh]] Missionary College in [[Ludhiana]], India. The [[magazine]] aims at the revival of [[Sikhism]] and preaching the message of the [[Sikh Gurus]]. It is the largest circulating Sikh religious monthly.

==History==
''Sikh Phulwari'' was started in Punjabi in August 1980.<ref name=pun>{{cite web|title=Profile of Sikh Missionary College|url=http://www.punjabcolleges.com/64599-indiacolleges-Sikh-Missionary-College-Ludhiana/|publisher=Punjab Colleges|accessdate=30 July 2015}}</ref> The Hindi edition of the magazine was launched later.<ref name=pun/>

